text: Dmitri Sergeyevich Kartashov (; born 26 August 1994) is a Russian football player who plays for FC Chayka Peschanokopskoye. ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Professional Football League for FC Chayka Peschanokopskoye on 28 July 2016 in a game against FC Biolog-Novokubansk. He made his Russian Football National League debut for Chayka on 13 July 2019 in a game against FC Fakel Voronezh. ==References== ==External links== * Profile by Russian Professional Football League Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:Association football midfielders
